121
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:39,570
Mm...

122
00:07:45,650 --> 00:07:46,870
Can I pwease listen to it now?

123
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:47,880
No.

124
00:07:49,650 --> 00:07:50,940
Pwease!

125
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,490
No.

126
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:00,220
Hey!

127
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:13,000
Should we go back to our room now?

128
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,890
Let's go back now.

129
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:22,620
♫If you're wondering about my persistence,♫

130
00:08:22,670 --> 00:08:23,780
You're such a flirt,

131
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,520
