132
00:08:25,530 --> 00:08:30,440
♫You don't have to stop
and think 'cause I've got it♫

133
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,970
♫I'll do whatever it takes to be close to you♫

134
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,990
♫I'll always be there, whatever you do♫

135
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:39,289
♫Yet you choose to ignore me♫

136
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:42,340
♫You never smile back at me whenever I do♫

137
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:44,830
♫You're like an exam,
'cause you never give me a clue♫

138
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,210
♫Constant dripping wears away the stone♫

139
00:08:47,250 --> 00:08:49,590
♫You'll see how our story goes♫

140
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:53,850
♫You've been my long-time crush,
yet the game never tires me♫

141
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:59,700
♫I'll give you my love every day, you see♫

142
00:09:45,850 --> 00:09:46,730
Ah,

143
