169
00:12:17,830 --> 00:12:19,130
This is just too much.

170
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,300
Give me your cheek.

171
00:12:28,300 --> 00:12:31,710
♫I can feel your heartbeat♫

172
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:35,110
♫Every time you breathe♫

173
00:12:35,130 --> 00:12:38,550
♫I don't know if we'll ever
get to have this moment again♫

174
00:12:38,590 --> 00:12:42,080
♫So please, don't leave this place♫

175
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,170
This is nice.

176
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:03,100
I like this kind of life,

177
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:07,120
one that's ordinary

178
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:09,460
and without any dreams.

179
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:13,040
Just keep on living,

180
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,150
enjoying the day, and living in the moment.

181
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:18,970
If I were to die tomorrow,

182
00:13:20,130 --> 00:13:22,010
I wouldn't feel incomplete.

183
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,140
How so?

184
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:25,990
Well...

185
00:13:27,290 --> 00:13:28,580
I don't know if you realize

186
00:13:31,650 --> 00:13:33,990
that those ordinary days of mine

187
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:36,040
are special because of you.

188
00:13:38,350 --> 00:13:39,710
And it's also you

189
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,880
