a cheat code before you were born,

193
00:13:49,190 --> 00:13:50,540
flawless

194
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:51,670
and perfect.

195
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,250
No.

196
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,840
I'm not all that good.

197
00:13:58,090 --> 00:14:00,640
I just have a habit of pressuring myself.

198
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,850
Let's say there are 100 points,

199
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,010
I'll make sure I get the full 100.

200
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:09,320
Sometimes, I think to myself

201
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,680
