202
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,620
even though the full mark is 100.

203
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:17,600
I just feel...

204
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,400
that I could do better.

205
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:25,590
Have I ever told you seriously

206
00:14:26,450 --> 00:14:27,770
that my dream

207
00:14:28,700 --> 00:14:30,800
is to succeed in jazz.

208
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:34,700
Isn't your dream to be a singer?

209
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:36,530
Mm...

210
00:14:37,230 --> 00:14:39,940
I haven't realized it until recently
that I like singing,

211
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:43,440
but I'm not the type to work
in front of the camera.

212
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:45,330
Maybe I could be...

213
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:46,800
a producer

214
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:48,410
working behind the scenes

215
00:14:48,690 --> 00:14:49,830
or something along the lines.

216
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:50,970
Okay.

217
00:14:52,090 --> 00:14:55,420
Then I'll live my life as an ordinary guy

218
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,940
