I'm not as cool as other people.

254
00:16:53,190 --> 00:16:54,860
I like how cute you are.

255
00:16:58,100 --> 00:17:00,360
I'm so lucky to have found you.

256
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:09,260
Wear this, baby.

257
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,550
No, I like it cold.

258
00:19:17,910 --> 00:19:19,220
Fine, I'll wear it.

259
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:24,020
Yay! You're the cutest.

260
