277
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:32,860
I brought some.

278
00:20:36,810 --> 00:20:38,120
Whoa!

279
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,370
You brought some for me?

280
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:42,560
Mm,

281
00:20:43,390 --> 00:20:45,210
I knew you'd go ham on the photos.

282
00:20:47,890 --> 00:20:48,780
Come on.

283
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,630
May I join you for tea?

284
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:33,190
Please do.

285
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:38,070
It's been such an honor.
Thank you for coming today.

286
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:04,810
Bathing in warm water in this cold

287
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:06,330
feels so relaxing.

288
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:08,240
Mm.

289
00:22:22,140 --> 00:22:23,230
Right,

290
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,310
about when we got a tattoo together,

291
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:31,270
why did you choose the moon and the beach?

292
00:22:36,100 --> 00:22:37,640
The moon doesn't suit you.

293
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:41,390
For me,

294
00:22:45,430 --> 00:22:46,640
you're the sun.

295
00:23:20,230 --> 00:23:21,040
What's up, bro?

296
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:24,220
Hello? Hm...

297
00:23:24,380 --> 00:23:25,660
Mm, I'm not gonna say a thing.

298
00:23:27,060 --> 00:23:28,880
What the fuck
is wrong with you again, Jamie?

299
00:23:29,140 --> 00:23:30,300
You're still there?

300
00:23:31,270 --> 00:23:33,320
Honestly, what are you
doing there for a week?

301
00:23:33,790 --> 00:23:35,550
Right! So when are you coming back?

302
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:38,120
When you have your own lover.

303
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:39,890
Bullshit.

304
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:43,270
You might as well relocate there

305
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:45,950
since you'll never
get to step foot in Nakhon Pathom again.

306
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:48,680
- I'm a warrior,
- "I'm a warrior,

307
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:50,590
- not a lover...
- not a lover!"

308
00:23:50,700 --> 00:23:51,320
Whoa!

309
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:53,110
How do you know I was gonna say that?

310
00:23:53,450 --> 00:23:55,190
Who wouldn't?
It's all you've ever said.

311
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:57,690
Yeah, even Tong and Kim know.

312
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,780
Qin!

313
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:02,220
Duang, let me talk to Qin first.

314
00:24:02,910 --> 00:24:04,520
Not a chance.

315
00:24:05,210 --> 00:24:05,950
Give it to me.

316
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:09,400
What is it, Jamie?

317
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:12,570
Qin, I miss you so much!

318
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:13,740
Where are you?

319
00:24:14,130 --> 00:24:15,870
Bangkok or Nakhon Pathom?

320
00:24:16,490 --> 00:24:18,120
In your heart.

321
00:24:18,630 --> 00:24:19,910
Seriously?

322
00:24:20,620 --> 00:24:21,720
How has it been, Qin?

323
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:22,960
Are you having fun on the trip?

324
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:24,360
Is Duang taking good care of you?

325
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:25,500
It is.

326
00:24:25,710 --> 00:24:26,660
I'm pretty happy.

327
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:30,620
Are you calling because you're not happy?

328
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:32,180
Jeez!

329
00:24:32,470 --> 00:24:34,190
You read me like a book.

330
00:24:36,860 --> 00:24:37,640
Qin.

331
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,160
What's up?

332
00:24:40,570 --> 00:24:41,950
What's the difference between

333
00:24:42,150 --> 00:24:43,280
being into someone and liking them?

334
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:46,950
Liking someone...

335
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:51,320
means you're okay
with having them or not.

336
00:24:52,340 --> 00:24:53,780
Maybe you feel a little bummed,

337
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,120
but you're not that sad

338
00:24:56,740 --> 00:24:58,700
since there are
so many people out there to like.

339
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:01,680
Being into someone

340
00:25:03,350 --> 00:25:04,510
is more specific.

341
00:25:05,870 --> 00:25:07,810
If you don't have them,
you'll be in tears.

342
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:11,300
But...if you love them,

343
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:15,870
it doesn't matter if you have them or not.

344
00:25:17,190 --> 00:25:18,640
You just wanna be there

345
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:20,380
to see their face every day,

346
00:25:21,170 --> 00:25:22,170
to feel,

347
00:25:23,450 --> 00:25:25,430
and to give, even when
you might get nothing in return.

348
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:29,570
Anything else, Jamie?

349
00:25:30,490 --> 00:25:31,940
That's everything, Qin.

350
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:33,960
I'll hang up now.
I've got the answer.

351
00:25:34,330 --> 00:25:35,280
Bye.

352
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:52,360
Jamie...

353
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:54,720
Is he going to become a lover?

354
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:57,520
Maybe.

355
00:25:58,250 --> 00:26:00,160
But I've always been a lover.

356
00:26:00,940 --> 00:26:01,940
You know that, don't you?

357
00:26:03,630 --> 00:26:05,980
Then would you love me hard tonight?

358
00:31:29,820 --> 00:31:30,820
Are you ready for me?

359
00:32:07,780 --> 00:32:09,850
Here come the Japanese snacks!

360
00:32:09,890 --> 00:32:11,460
- Whoa!
- Hey!

361
00:32:15,190 --> 00:32:15,920
Whoa!

362
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:17,290
Whoa!

363
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:22,840
Three, two, one, go!

364
00:32:24,420 --> 00:32:26,360
Don't be so possessive, Prachai!

365
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:27,950
Look in the mirror, Jettana!

366
00:32:27,990 --> 00:32:29,840
- Give me that!
- Hey!

367
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,670
Can't you just share?

368
00:32:31,770 --> 00:32:32,850
You fight like babies.

369
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:42,240
Right, Duang,

370
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,310
while you were in Japan,

371
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:46,260
this bastard disappeared
to who-knows-where for four to five days.

372
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:49,390
He even refused to tell me where!

373
00:32:49,730 --> 00:32:51,640
Something is definitely up.

374
00:32:52,710 --> 00:32:53,570
What?!

375
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:56,520
Just a warrior
going into battle, like always.

376
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,700
I'm confident while I say it.

377
00:32:57,740 --> 00:32:59,240
If this warrior ever turns to a lover,

378
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,140
you can come smack me.

379
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:01,040
I'm with Pae.

380
00:33:01,100 --> 00:33:02,790
What?! Duang!

381
00:33:06,370 --> 00:33:07,610
So how was Japan?

382
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,640
Huh?

383
00:33:08,990 --> 00:33:09,860
As expected,

384
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:12,140
it's a honeymoon trip,
so of course, it's marvelous!

385
00:33:12,910 --> 00:33:14,060
Would you stop flexing?

386
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:18,600
Aren't you a sore loser?

387
00:33:20,700 --> 00:33:21,330
Ugh!

388
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:23,080
I'll devour this whole damn thing!

389
00:33:24,650 --> 00:33:26,120
- Whoa!
- Let go!

390
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,850
Let go of me!

391
00:33:31,210 --> 00:33:32,080
Hey! Time out...

392
00:33:34,780 --> 00:33:36,560
Qin texted. Qin texted me.

393
00:33:46,830 --> 00:33:47,830
When does your class end?

394
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:51,480
At 4. I'll be right back.

395
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,660
Call me when class is over.

396
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:00,780
Argh! What?!

397
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:03,040
Bro, wait! I haven't shown this one off!

398
00:34:15,900 --> 00:34:16,699
Uh, excuse me.

399
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:23,000
Can I sing for this year's Freshy Night?

400
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:24,790
That's a good idea.

401
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:27,010
What are you gonna play? Jazz?

402
00:34:29,290 --> 00:34:31,510
I wanna sing the song I wrote for Duang.

403
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:34,449
Aw... Qin!

404
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:36,090
That's so sweet.

405
00:34:36,159 --> 00:34:37,210
I'm looking forward to it.

406
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:39,870
Then, please excuse me.

407
00:34:44,310 --> 00:34:45,760
Right, guys.

408
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,650
Thank you...

409
00:34:50,739 --> 00:34:52,380
for letting me sing onstage last year.

410
00:35:08,890 --> 00:35:10,180
Are you done with your class?

411
00:35:10,330 --> 00:35:11,340
Hurry back.

412
00:35:11,890 --> 00:35:12,890
I'm getting lonely.

413
00:35:13,370 --> 00:35:15,770
How can you be so cute when you're fussy,

414
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:17,350
my Qin?

415
00:35:18,720 --> 00:35:19,650
Hurry up.

416
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:20,680
There's a surprise for you.

417
00:35:21,970 --> 00:35:22,980
Surprise...

418
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,480
What surprise, baby?

419
00:35:25,540 --> 00:35:28,210
How is it a surprise if I tell you?

420
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:31,010
Hurry back and drive safely.

421
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:31,830
Alright.

422
00:35:36,810 --> 00:35:37,810
I've gotta go.

423
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,900
Off to Qin again, huh?

424
00:35:40,380 --> 00:35:41,610
Do I still have to say it?

425
00:35:41,930 --> 00:35:43,400
I'm a lover boy.

426
00:35:43,990 --> 00:35:44,780
I'm off.

427
00:35:48,770 --> 00:35:51,130
- Yeah, me too.
- What?

428
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:52,550
Where are you going?

429
00:35:52,690 --> 00:35:53,930
Not the same way he's going.

430
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,330
- Bye.
- What?

431
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:01,450
I don't think
his lover boy era is too far away.

432
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,140
I'm back!

433
00:36:11,910 --> 00:36:14,010
Say hi to Uncle.

434
00:36:15,810 --> 00:36:16,810
You!

435
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:19,560
Don't be loud!
She's gonna get startled.

436
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:23,680
Look.

437
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:31,220
I'm gonna cry...

438
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:34,510
Isn't she cute?

439
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:36,400
Absolutely.

440
00:36:38,340 --> 00:36:39,650
Good.

441
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:42,690
Uncle is a good guy, see?

442
00:36:58,070 --> 00:37:00,030
What made you decide to buy her, hm?!

443
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:01,340
Yesterday,

444
00:37:01,370 --> 00:37:03,520
I sent a friend to a corgi farm,

445
00:37:04,110 --> 00:37:05,920
and they sent me a video.

446
00:37:06,050 --> 00:37:08,120
This one clicked the most.

447
00:37:10,050 --> 00:37:12,210
Tell me, how much was she?

448
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:13,780
Seven...

449
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,060
7,000?!

450
00:37:16,170 --> 00:37:17,480
70,000

451
00:37:19,690 --> 00:37:21,620
70,000...

452
00:37:22,910 --> 00:37:25,620
The reason I picked this one
was that she doesn't bark at all.

453
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:29,460
Also, she makes funny faces,
so I decided on her.

454
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:30,850
He's just like me.

455
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:33,890
You...

456
00:37:33,990 --> 00:37:35,990
You're melting me.

457
00:37:37,250 --> 00:37:40,830
Why do you have to be so gentle
and such an animal lover?

458
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:43,950
I'm head over heels in love with you.

459
00:37:44,630 --> 00:37:46,450
Really now, Uncle?

460
00:37:49,080 --> 00:37:50,930
But it's still 70,000 baht.

461
00:37:51,310 --> 00:37:53,390
I know you're rich,

462
00:37:53,530 --> 00:37:55,850
but you still have to save up.

463
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:57,860
A purchase like this

464
00:37:58,610 --> 00:38:00,450
would give me a heart attack.

465
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:02,280
What money will I have to spoil you with?

466
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,250
I'm not asking you to spoil me.

467
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:14,470
- Qin,
- Hm?

468
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:16,000
what is her name?

469
00:38:17,410 --> 00:38:18,600
Hm...

470
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,610
I haven't come up with one.

471
00:38:22,050 --> 00:38:23,710
What should we name you, sweetie?

472
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:25,660
Why are you so fluffy? Hm?!

473
00:38:28,870 --> 00:38:30,280
How about Khonfoo?

474
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:31,190
Whoa!

475
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:32,440
Are you gonna go with that name?

476
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:36,280
Well, she's cute and fluffy,
which is Khonfoo.

477
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:39,150
Whoa!

478
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:42,160
Hey, she barked!

479
00:38:42,600 --> 00:38:45,190
Is that your name, sweetie?

480
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,600
You're the cutest.

481
00:38:54,420 --> 00:38:57,650
Wait, if I'm Uncle,

482
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,460
what are you?

483
00:39:00,790 --> 00:39:02,170
I'm Papa, of course.

484
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:04,500
What?! But I'm your boyfriend.

485
00:39:04,690 --> 00:39:05,470
So Uncle, it is.

486
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:07,380
But I wanna be his papa!

487
00:39:07,540 --> 00:39:08,690
Then,

488
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:12,020
you'll have to take Khonfoo
to get vaccinated

489
00:39:12,170 --> 00:39:16,290
and take her
on a walk when I don't have time.

490
00:39:17,820 --> 00:39:20,470
So that's all it takes to be his papa?

491
00:39:21,740 --> 00:39:23,640
"Love me tons, too."

492
00:39:29,890 --> 00:39:31,260
So small,

493
00:39:31,610 --> 00:39:33,260
yet already a papa.

494
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,670
I'm as big as you are.

495
00:39:37,510 --> 00:39:39,330
You're giving me cute aggression.

496
00:39:39,370 --> 00:39:42,830
Who in the world
could be even cuter than a puppy?

497
00:39:43,650 --> 00:39:45,110
Get your face off of me.

498
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,170
I'm gonna look at my daughter.

499
00:39:52,010 --> 00:39:53,770
She got you so hooked.

500
00:39:53,810 --> 00:39:55,520
I guess I'm not important anymore?

501
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:56,960
Delusional.

502
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:58,590
This is our daughter, you know?

503
00:40:00,270 --> 00:40:02,890
You're the cutest.

504
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:07,640
You really are cute.

505
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:11,290
Right, Duang.

506
00:40:11,650 --> 00:40:14,020
- Hm?
- Give me a hand here.

507
00:40:17,190 --> 00:40:18,770
How do you set this up?

508
00:40:19,170 --> 00:40:21,150
Mm...

509
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:33,260
Boo!

510
00:40:35,930 --> 00:40:39,170
- Get in your house first.
- Here, this is how it's done.

511
00:41:05,890 --> 00:41:07,130
Hey!

512
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:08,870
Come to bed.

513
00:41:18,090 --> 00:41:19,090
Duang.

514
00:41:21,430 --> 00:41:23,550
Let's have Khonfoo sleep with us.

515
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:26,960
Please, please, please.

516
00:41:27,700 --> 00:41:29,620
No can do.

517
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:34,580
We need to train her
to sleep in her place!

518
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:36,280
We agreed on that, didn't we?

519
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,290
Please...

520
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:09,360
Don't pull that one on me.

521
00:42:09,580 --> 00:42:10,960
I won't look at you!

522
00:42:13,590 --> 00:42:15,440
Are you jealous even of our own child?

523
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:18,070
If she sleeps in this bed,

524
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:19,890
you won't cuddle with me!

525
00:42:19,930 --> 00:42:21,270
You're jealous.

526
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:22,860
Sure!

527
00:42:44,080 --> 00:42:45,520
You're possessive of me;

528
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:47,300
I'm also possessive of you.

529
00:42:54,160 --> 00:42:55,980
You said there was
only one of me in this world;

530
00:42:56,940 --> 00:42:58,710
there's also
only one of you in this world.

531
00:42:59,340 --> 00:43:01,130
If I don't cuddle with you,

532
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:03,050
who would I cuddle with?

533
00:43:05,750 --> 00:43:07,870
If you keep this up,

534
00:43:08,450 --> 00:43:10,630
I'll get up and kiss you,

535
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:13,590
and you won't get to go anywhere.

536
00:43:14,250 --> 00:43:15,750
This is final.

537
00:43:18,290 --> 00:43:19,690
You think I'm scared?

538
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:29,550
Khonfoo!

539
00:43:30,610 --> 00:43:31,610
What?!

540
00:43:31,830 --> 00:43:32,890
You...

541
00:43:47,390 --> 00:43:49,180
How nice that
we get to be with each other.

542
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:54,890
What's really
on your mind when you say that?

543
00:43:58,260 --> 00:43:59,230
Do you know?

544
00:44:01,140 --> 00:44:02,660
At this time last year,

545
00:44:03,230 --> 00:44:04,970
I was also sleepless.

546
00:44:05,900 --> 00:44:09,730
Just thinking that I'd meet, talk to you,

547
00:44:11,200 --> 00:44:13,260
and ask to be in your world the next day,

548
00:44:15,640 --> 00:44:17,110
it all felt so difficult.

549
00:44:18,490 --> 00:44:20,350
I was only smol, you know.

550
00:44:23,570 --> 00:44:26,630
I didn't know
if I'd have to drown my sorrows

551
00:44:27,610 --> 00:44:30,230
in beer every day if you rejected me.

552
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:33,190
Who told you to be that lovesick?

553
00:44:34,180 --> 00:44:35,040
Right?

554
00:44:36,460 --> 00:44:38,440
Only one look at you,
and my heart flew away.

555
00:44:41,860 --> 00:44:42,860
But you do know

556
00:44:43,310 --> 00:44:44,760
that I noticed you first.

557
00:44:47,720 --> 00:44:50,200
You can keep it to yourself.

558
00:44:50,370 --> 00:44:52,130
Not me, though.

559
00:44:59,590 --> 00:45:01,090
I love you, Qin.

560
00:45:04,230 --> 00:45:05,770
I love you...

561
00:45:06,090 --> 00:45:07,050
very much.

562
00:45:12,220 --> 00:45:13,780
I'll love you even more.

563
00:45:14,490 --> 00:45:15,490
Can I?

564
00:45:19,550 --> 00:45:21,170
It's Loy Krathong again tomorrow.

565
00:45:23,710 --> 00:45:24,930
Last year,

566
00:45:25,010 --> 00:45:26,490
I asked to win your heart.

567
00:45:27,190 --> 00:45:28,190
This year, though,

568
00:45:29,510 --> 00:45:31,790
can I float my krathong with you?

569
00:45:34,520 --> 00:45:36,310
I'll let you do it with me every year.

570
00:45:36,690 --> 00:45:37,780
How does that sound?

571
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:39,640
I'm down.

572
00:45:40,430 --> 00:45:41,560
Every year, right?

573
00:45:42,280 --> 00:45:43,110
Mm.

574
00:45:45,920 --> 00:45:47,120
Your class is about to begin.

575
00:45:47,780 --> 00:45:48,830
Stay focused in class.

576
00:45:52,030 --> 00:45:53,640
Qin!

577
00:45:53,740 --> 00:45:55,610
I miss you so much...

578
00:45:56,190 --> 00:45:57,750
Go away! Shoo!

579
00:45:59,100 --> 00:46:00,100
You're getting him all dirty.

580
00:46:00,490 --> 00:46:01,820
Are you alright?

581
00:46:02,130 --> 00:46:03,550
Did you catch anything dirty?

582
00:46:03,830 --> 00:46:07,130
Jeez... Damn you, Cheewin!

583
00:46:07,250 --> 00:46:09,370
I'm a person, not some germs!

584
00:46:10,080 --> 00:46:10,970
Ooh!

585
00:46:11,290 --> 00:46:14,520
You're being too much, Jamie.
They're boyfriends.

586
00:46:14,600 --> 00:46:16,830
Yeah, you don't know any better!

587
00:46:17,540 --> 00:46:18,690
Ugh!

588
00:46:25,220 --> 00:46:25,970
Hey.

589
00:46:30,780 --> 00:46:32,820
Right, I just realized
that today is Loy Krathong

590
00:46:33,130 --> 00:46:35,080
after seeing other students
setting up stalls to sell omelets.

591
00:46:35,260 --> 00:46:37,270
This year, Loy Krathong
arrives before the Freshy Night.

592
00:46:37,540 --> 00:46:39,900
- How could you not know what today is?
- What?

593
00:46:40,430 --> 00:46:43,330
Right, are you
gonna go float krathongs tonight?

594
00:46:43,700 --> 00:46:44,770
Let me come with you.

595
00:46:44,960 --> 00:46:47,670
Damn, no one
asked me to the festival this year.

596
00:46:47,700 --> 00:46:49,010
Mm.

597
00:46:50,350 --> 00:46:51,520
Mm...

598
00:46:51,760 --> 00:46:52,840
Come with us.

599
00:46:53,590 --> 00:46:54,840
I think I'll go with Qin,

600
00:46:54,930 --> 00:46:56,290
and these two will come with us.

601
00:46:59,600 --> 00:47:02,160
So, no girls have asked you this year?

602
00:47:02,240 --> 00:47:03,390
No.

603
00:47:03,710 --> 00:47:05,400
But there was, last year.

604
00:47:06,640 --> 00:47:08,910
A girl DMed me
and invited me to float a krathong with her.

605
00:47:08,940 --> 00:47:10,700
Ooh...

606
00:47:12,290 --> 00:47:15,130
So what was her name? Was it Cherry?

607
00:47:15,450 --> 00:47:16,360
Yes.

608
00:47:17,380 --> 00:47:19,370
Wait, how do you know?

609
00:47:28,340 --> 00:47:30,500
I am Cherry.

610
00:47:30,750 --> 00:47:32,430
I am Cherry...

611
00:47:32,470 --> 00:47:34,140
I am Cherry.

612
00:47:34,170 --> 00:47:36,760
I am Cherry...

613
00:47:39,460 --> 00:47:43,360
[Please give some time for Tong]

614
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:54,790
- Sorry, bro.
- Mm, sorry, bro.

615
00:47:57,140 --> 00:47:58,760
You bastards!

616
00:47:59,150 --> 00:47:59,760
Ooh!

617
00:47:59,970 --> 00:48:02,640
I'll beat you guys like a drum.

618
00:48:03,010 --> 00:48:04,200
Bastards, come here!

619
00:48:04,550 --> 00:48:05,570
Hey!

620
00:48:05,600 --> 00:48:06,600
Pae!

621
00:48:09,520 --> 00:48:10,710
No, no, no, don't hit me!

622
00:48:15,270 --> 00:48:16,860
Hey, hey, Jamie!

623
00:48:16,890 --> 00:48:19,330
- Help me!
- Hey! It's Duang!

624
00:48:19,740 --> 00:48:21,530
Over there! Go!

625
00:48:21,900 --> 00:48:24,070
I'm not gonna float
my krathong with you anymore, bastards.

626
00:48:40,550 --> 00:48:42,870
Aw, baby...

627
00:48:42,950 --> 00:48:44,730
It's the Loy Krathong festival.

628
00:48:47,380 --> 00:48:50,420
- These two are so lovely-dovey.
- True.

629
00:48:50,460 --> 00:48:52,620
The pond is turning into syrup now.

630
00:48:53,130 --> 00:48:55,990
I can't believe that
Qin has a boyfriend, either.

631
00:48:56,030 --> 00:48:57,030
Right.

632
00:48:57,060 --> 00:48:58,450
They even have a child now,

633
00:48:58,490 --> 00:49:01,130
even though it's a corgi.

634
00:49:02,600 --> 00:49:04,480
Right, so where is Tong?

635
00:49:04,660 --> 00:49:07,500
Man, that one got so sulky
that he went home.

636
00:49:08,300 --> 00:49:10,400
Jeez, that's alright.
I'll make up with him.

637
00:49:10,550 --> 00:49:11,670
Hey,

638
00:49:13,340 --> 00:49:16,720
I'm so happy that
I'll finally float my krathong with you.

639
00:49:17,650 --> 00:49:19,280
I'm blushing now.

640
00:49:20,710 --> 00:49:22,470
"I'll finally float my krathong with you..."

641
00:49:22,510 --> 00:49:23,970
You always blush.

642
00:49:24,120 --> 00:49:26,410
Get used to having me by your side.

643
00:49:27,130 --> 00:49:30,240
Whoa, I could literally die...

644
00:49:31,930 --> 00:49:35,150
Okay, I'll spend forever with you.

645
00:49:41,250 --> 00:49:42,560
Not today, Satan.

646
00:49:43,090 --> 00:49:44,530
- Let's go.
- Absolutely not.

647
00:49:44,600 --> 00:49:45,600
Gosh, Pae,

648
00:49:46,010 --> 00:49:47,190
bestie.

649
00:50:42,890 --> 00:50:44,250
I have something I wanna give you.

650
00:50:45,900 --> 00:50:46,410
Hm?

651
00:50:47,520 --> 00:50:48,410
What is it?

652
00:50:54,560 --> 00:50:56,170
[Duang With You]

653
00:50:56,210 --> 00:50:57,280
This is Duang,

654
00:50:57,420 --> 00:50:58,420
and this is you.

655
00:51:00,060 --> 00:51:01,850
"Duang With You."

656
00:51:04,290 --> 00:51:06,160
Here, take a look.

657
00:51:14,400 --> 00:51:16,210
"Hey, my buddy likes you."

658
00:51:18,250 --> 00:51:19,360
My name is 'Buddy.'

659
00:51:28,020 --> 00:51:30,010
"Can I walk you home?"

660
00:51:40,510 --> 00:51:41,510
This one,

661
00:51:41,540 --> 00:51:44,420
I didn't say anything, just following you.

662
00:51:50,730 --> 00:51:52,400
This is when I liked watching you eat

663
00:51:52,880 --> 00:51:54,120
so that I can get your order right.

664
00:52:04,430 --> 00:52:05,890
If I don't ask you now,

665
00:52:06,740 --> 00:52:08,410
I'll probably go insane.

666
00:52:10,970 --> 00:52:12,510
"Will you be my boyfriend?"

667
00:52:14,210 --> 00:52:16,910
Aw...you!

668
00:52:17,590 --> 00:52:18,590
Will you?

669
00:52:18,740 --> 00:52:20,730
Wait, we already are.

670
00:52:28,160 --> 00:52:29,160
Phew...

671
00:52:29,430 --> 00:52:31,090
This is your monthiversary gift.

672
00:52:32,050 --> 00:52:35,500
There are still so many pictures inside,
so be sure to look at them.

673
00:52:37,120 --> 00:52:38,200
You must spend a long time on it.

674
00:52:39,320 --> 00:52:40,440
Well, the entire year.

675
00:52:40,860 --> 00:52:41,960
Do you like it?

676
00:52:44,140 --> 00:52:46,150
Thank you
for putting so much thought into it.

677
00:52:46,820 --> 00:52:49,110
Can you do it
for this year's Freshy Night, too?

678
00:52:49,200 --> 00:52:50,510
I'll be onstage.

679
00:52:52,760 --> 00:52:54,110
Totally!

680
00:52:54,680 --> 00:52:57,640
I'll be cheering you on
right by the stage.

681
00:53:00,210 --> 00:53:03,670
I'm looking forward to it.
I have a gift prepared for you, too.

682
00:53:05,710 --> 00:53:06,790
A gift?

683
00:53:07,750 --> 00:53:09,720
What gift?

684
00:53:09,850 --> 00:53:11,390
I wanna know!

685
00:53:12,020 --> 00:53:13,150
I'm not telling you.

686
00:53:16,420 --> 00:53:17,710
Wait.

687
00:53:23,190 --> 00:53:24,710
How freaking cute.

688
00:53:29,570 --> 00:53:30,810
Come on, guys.

689
00:53:30,850 --> 00:53:31,950
Cheers.

690
00:53:32,000 --> 00:53:33,110
It's my treat today.

691
00:53:33,410 --> 00:53:37,510
Celebrate Duang
having a boyfriend! Cheers!

692
00:53:37,530 --> 00:53:40,300
- I want me a lover, too!
- Wow...

693
00:53:40,320 --> 00:53:41,520
- Bottoms up.
- Thank you, bro.

694
00:53:41,860 --> 00:53:42,540
Anytime.

695
00:53:42,580 --> 00:53:45,790
- This Nakhon Pathom lover boy is my pal.
- Wow, that's wicked.

696
00:53:47,730 --> 00:53:48,990
Drink up. Fill it to the brim.

697
00:53:51,940 --> 00:53:52,990
Don't hold back.

698
00:53:53,290 --> 00:53:54,760
My tummy is already filled to the brim.

699
00:54:06,840 --> 00:54:07,870
Hey, Qin.

700
00:54:10,200 --> 00:54:11,240
Duang.

701
00:54:24,400 --> 00:54:25,480
Wanna go say hi to them?

702
00:54:26,700 --> 00:54:28,800
Hm... No.

703
00:54:28,850 --> 00:54:29,820
I'll use the restroom.

704
00:54:38,090 --> 00:54:39,540
- Oh! Ow...
- Ouch!

705
00:54:39,780 --> 00:54:40,970
I'm sorry!

706
00:54:43,100 --> 00:54:45,600
Ma'am, please don't do this.
My boyfriend won't like it.

707
00:54:45,630 --> 00:54:47,930
I'm too wasted. I can't...

708
00:54:48,600 --> 00:54:49,600
Sorry...

709
00:54:59,580 --> 00:55:01,440
I'm sorry. I'm drunk.

710
00:55:06,040 --> 00:55:07,930
I don't know him. I don't.

711
00:55:15,250 --> 00:55:17,280
Can you not let anyone
get close like that again?

712
00:55:17,830 --> 00:55:19,950
I don't wanna come off as unlovely to you.

713
00:55:21,250 --> 00:55:23,400
I'm sure you'll always be lovely,

714
00:55:23,620 --> 00:55:25,250
from the start

715
00:55:25,600 --> 00:55:28,240
until forever!

716
00:55:28,570 --> 00:55:30,900
Make sure it doesn't happen again next time.

717
00:55:31,470 --> 00:55:32,870
Your wish is my command!

718
00:55:33,870 --> 00:55:36,140
I'm not even sure
if I should be jealous or annoyed.

719
00:55:36,340 --> 00:55:38,590
These two are so adorable
that they don't even fight.

720
00:55:41,590 --> 00:55:42,990
- Let's cheers, man.
- Come on.

721
00:55:43,800 --> 00:55:44,800
That's true.

722
00:55:45,070 --> 00:55:46,070
You're jealous of them, huh?

723
00:55:46,550 --> 00:55:47,550
Wanna go to the restroom?

724
00:55:47,940 --> 00:55:49,320
- Let's go.
- Come on.

725
00:55:49,360 --> 00:55:50,450
Well, well, well.

726
00:55:52,900 --> 00:55:54,310
- Excuse me.
- Please.

727
00:56:27,360 --> 00:56:28,590
Don't smile.

728
00:56:29,910 --> 00:56:32,810
So I can't even smile now? That's sad.

729
00:56:44,690 --> 00:56:45,800
It's good.

730
00:56:46,910 --> 00:56:48,120
Want a taste?

731
00:56:56,700 --> 00:56:57,980
Jettana.

732
00:57:02,400 --> 00:57:03,450
What say you?

733
00:57:26,210 --> 00:57:27,320
"What say you"?

734
00:57:29,040 --> 00:57:29,900
Oh...

735
00:57:30,570 --> 00:57:31,800
My bad, my bad.

736
00:57:31,890 --> 00:57:33,610
I won't use complicated words anymore.

737
00:57:33,730 --> 00:57:37,370
It's how the Northerners say, "What's up?"

738
00:57:38,220 --> 00:57:39,280
Okay,

739
00:57:40,150 --> 00:57:41,090
what say you?

740
00:57:44,790 --> 00:57:46,050
I say nothing.

741
00:57:46,120 --> 00:57:47,190
Please.

742
00:58:05,080 --> 00:58:07,270
After the laps,
let's have guay jap yuan.

743
00:58:07,580 --> 00:58:10,320
I don't know what it is,
but I don't mind tagging along.

744
00:58:11,040 --> 00:58:12,980
How come you've been
accepting my invitation so easily?

745
00:58:15,450 --> 00:58:19,040
I'm not saying you're easy,
and I'd never think that way.

746
00:58:20,290 --> 00:58:21,520
Maybe it's kindred spirits.

747
00:58:25,580 --> 00:58:27,990
Wow! You know such fancy words.

748
00:58:28,410 --> 00:58:29,300
Praise me.

749
00:58:31,480 --> 00:58:34,450
Amazing job, gorgeous little pookie.

750
00:58:36,200 --> 00:58:37,200
"Gorgeous little pookie"?

751
00:58:38,280 --> 00:58:39,280
It's like...

752
00:58:39,620 --> 00:58:41,880
a term to call someone you adore.

753
00:58:41,960 --> 00:58:44,760
Normally, the word "gorgeous"
is traditionally used with girls, right?

754
00:58:44,920 --> 00:58:47,440
Mm, as far as I know.

755
00:58:47,820 --> 00:58:50,490
Nowadays, it can be used
to call anyone you adore,

756
00:58:50,530 --> 00:58:52,660
- like...
- Gorgeous Jamie?

757
00:58:59,690 --> 00:59:01,070
Was I wrong?

758
00:59:01,340 --> 00:59:02,960
Do you wanna see tears?

759
00:59:04,560 --> 00:59:05,560
Whose tears?

760
00:59:06,980 --> 00:59:09,710
Let's keep running.
This conversation's making me wanna cry.

761
00:59:10,060 --> 00:59:11,370
Fine, I'm sorry.

762
00:59:12,110 --> 00:59:13,790
Smooch my cheek, and I'll feel better.

763
00:59:22,700 --> 00:59:23,840
Are we good?

764
00:59:27,630 --> 00:59:29,840
Don't you do that
with just anyone, got it?

765
00:59:35,790 --> 00:59:38,400
Liking someone
means you're fine with having them or not.

766
00:59:38,410 --> 00:59:41,020
You're probably bummed, but not regretful.
Lock that in, Jamie.

767
00:59:43,090 --> 00:59:44,430
Wait up!

768
00:59:50,110 --> 00:59:51,110
Feel like it now?

769
00:59:51,770 --> 00:59:53,730
Uh... Right here?

770
00:59:54,580 --> 00:59:56,240
Are we talking about the same stuff?

771
00:59:57,120 --> 00:59:58,830
I hate you!

772
00:59:59,270 --> 01:00:00,860
You don't.

773
01:00:01,300 --> 01:00:02,440
What did you say?

774
01:00:04,000 --> 01:00:05,460
What did you say to me?

775
01:00:05,610 --> 01:00:06,840
"You don't"!

776
01:00:09,180 --> 01:00:10,960
Get over here!

777
01:00:19,000 --> 01:00:20,200
Thank you.

778
01:00:21,600 --> 01:00:23,210
Jamie, are you holding up fine?

779
01:00:23,690 --> 01:00:25,620
That's so insulting!

780
01:00:26,700 --> 01:00:28,320
Well, you do look really tired.

781
01:00:29,320 --> 01:00:31,520
You're too good at running, though.

782
01:00:33,690 --> 01:00:36,130
When I get stressed out,
I like working out.

783
01:00:36,160 --> 01:00:38,990
That running was a joke.

784
01:00:39,780 --> 01:00:41,510
"A joke."

785
01:00:43,090 --> 01:00:44,370
What a teaser.

786
01:01:00,410 --> 01:01:01,330
That's done.

787
01:01:04,620 --> 01:01:06,560
Let's go eat
the thing you told me earlier.

788
01:01:07,210 --> 01:01:08,300
Ugh...

789
01:01:09,390 --> 01:01:10,840
I'm so tired.

790
01:01:11,990 --> 01:01:15,250
Come on, Jettana. Hurry up, Jettana.

791
01:01:15,920 --> 01:01:17,330
Come here, Jettana!

792
01:01:18,810 --> 01:01:20,220
What is this about?!

793
01:01:20,930 --> 01:01:21,960
What?!

794
01:01:39,910 --> 01:01:45,080
[Found]

795
01:02:11,670 --> 01:02:13,040
Right, guys.

796
01:02:13,310 --> 01:02:15,510
Earlier, I saw someone drinking
chrysanthemum tea at the faculty building.

797
01:02:15,570 --> 01:02:17,560
He dressed so nicely.

798
01:02:18,850 --> 01:02:20,220
I can back him up on that.

799
01:02:20,920 --> 01:02:23,910
He turned the entire faculty's heads.
I'm confused.

800
01:02:24,430 --> 01:02:26,890
Who is he?
Is he even from planet Earth?

801
01:02:26,930 --> 01:02:28,960
It's better than one could imagine,

802
01:02:29,410 --> 01:02:31,060
maybe even better than the wildest dream.

803
01:02:31,520 --> 01:02:33,200
Maybe he's a tourist?

804
01:02:33,260 --> 01:02:35,930
In what fucking world does a tourist
just lounge under the Music building?

805
01:02:36,040 --> 01:02:37,040
Are you nuts?

806
01:02:38,000 --> 01:02:40,160
Is it someone who dresses stylishly?

807
01:02:41,100 --> 01:02:42,940
- Yeah.
- Bingo. That's the one.

808
01:02:43,080 --> 01:02:45,560
Oh...

809
01:02:46,040 --> 01:02:47,520
He's waiting at the wrong building.

810
01:02:49,780 --> 01:02:51,680
- How would you know?
- Yeah.

811
01:02:54,440 --> 01:02:56,220
There you are.

812
01:03:11,740 --> 01:03:13,140
Jamie.

813
01:03:25,610 --> 01:03:27,110
Let me introduce you to him.

814
01:03:27,750 --> 01:03:29,080
This is Marvis.

815
01:03:31,810 --> 01:03:33,680
Uh... Hello!

816
01:03:34,130 --> 01:03:35,210
This is Duang.

817
01:03:35,450 --> 01:03:36,450
That one is Pae.

818
01:03:37,090 --> 01:03:38,250
That's Tong and Kim.

819
01:03:38,590 --> 01:03:41,080
And this...is Qin,
the one I was telling you about.

820
01:03:42,340 --> 01:03:43,750
Hello.

821
01:03:43,780 --> 01:03:46,320
You can just call me Mar. I won't bite.

822
01:03:47,000 --> 01:03:50,490
Jamie, you're something else,
you know that?!

823
01:03:50,750 --> 01:03:52,060
My heart was sinking there...

824
01:03:52,470 --> 01:03:54,720
Are you feeling sick? Are you okay?

825
01:03:56,120 --> 01:03:58,140
I am okay. I am.

826
01:03:58,300 --> 01:04:00,490
You really teased him there.

827
01:04:00,520 --> 01:04:02,820
That one's already so unique.

828
01:04:02,980 --> 01:04:04,890
I wasn't teasing him,

829
01:04:04,940 --> 01:04:06,390
just simply saying hi.

830
